{"tid":1165213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次遊行6月9日我一定會去","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:16:34.000Z","uid":161664,"like":143,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"005f70edc0c792bc6b775ae8b64da34f7427a4d3","tid":1165213,"uid":161664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"民陣表示，將於6月9日舉行遊行，以回應保安局局長李家超把《逃犯條例》修訂草案，直接提交大會並恢復二讀辯論。召集人岑子杰表示，目標是有30萬人參與遊行。<br />\n<br />\n民陣預計遊行在當日下午3時集合，由銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道。<br />\n<br />\n可能今次，會係最後一次<br />\n6月12如果二讀成功後，三讀應該半個月內搞掂。<br />\n為咗自己 身邊嘅屋企人 朋友 下一代<br />\n唔好再話返工不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借用隔黎po, 睇完陳太條片<br />\n<br />\n香港人，今次真係要行出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7d6fbf8e446a99dd114e7268c17947ec4bde6b","tid":1165213,"uid":35505,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"就算唔講政治，會唔會拉果啲野<br />\n通過咗，香港經濟實仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b20b03363b860fb12b76f61cc983f3f58cc14","tid":1165213,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"不了，攬炒"},{"pid":"7f24fb171dc7f7c444ea4f3e618df53b87635b9e","tid":1165213,"uid":78791,"like":6,"dislike":32,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b846ac6cd93642a9d64b4c3d7b24e435d2de5629","tid":1165213,"uid":161664,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"唔去嗰d全部大陸種"},{"pid":"43bec7333c593474f8cd2f7100c2c749d26beb48","tid":1165213,"uid":127988,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"去果一日有用咩, 睇下台灣, 南韓日日示威, 憑你班港喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac04efae06ba016745164b0ca8e2f9e241733010","tid":1165213,"uid":229886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"43bec7333c593474f8cd2f7100c2c749d